(4) Barber school or college
shall mean an establishment properly licensed and operated for the teaching
and training of barber students;

(6) Manager shall mean a licensed
barber having control of the barber shop and of the persons working or employed
therein;

(9) Assistant barber instructor
shall mean a teacher of the barbering trade registered as an assistant barber
instructor as required by the act;

(10) Registered or licensed
barber shall mean a person who has completed the requirements to receive a
certificate as a barber and to whom a certificate has been issued;
